research reveals that the polarization of the radiation arising from the\ntransitions between fine and hyperfine states of the ground level can provide a\nunique diagnostics of magnetic fields in the Epoch of Reionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2013 22:26:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-15"}
