orus does not due to\nthe significant energy released. The total number of H observed by Cassini\ninside 5 RS: our modeling results suggest ~20% from dissociation in the\nEnceladus torus, ~10% from dissociation of ring H2 atmosphere, and ~50% from\nTitan H torus implying that ~20% comes from the Saturnian atmosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2013 22:55:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
